        "text": "The document is a table of contents for the \"NYISO Capacity Market Products\" and includes the following attachments:\n\n- **Attachment A**: Installed Capacity Event Schedule\n- **Attachment B**: Locational Minimum Installed Capacity Requirements/Maximum Allowances of External Installed Capacity\n- **Attachment C**: Maps of the NYCA Transmission Districts and Zones\n- **Attachment D**: DMNC Test Supplemental Information Form\n- **Attachment E**: Grandfathered External Installed Capacity Agreements\n- **Attachment F**: Agreement to Purchase or Sell Unforced Capacity in NYISO Installed Capacity Auctions\n- **Attachment G**: Notification Template\n- **Attachment H**: NYISO Administered Installed Capacity Auctions: Illustrations of Market-Clearing Price Calculations\n- **Attachment I**: Miscellaneous Auction Procedures\n- **Attachment J**: Unforced Capacity for Installed Capacity Suppliers\n- **Attachment K**: Reportable Operating Data\n- **Attachment L**: Revisions in Transmission Owner Installed Capacity Data Submittals\n- **Attachment M**: Procedure to Apply for a Capacity Limited Resource (CLR), Energy Limited Resource (ELR), Ambient Condition-Dependent Classification and/or for an Energy Duration Limitation\n- **Attachment N**: Procedure to Calculate Translation Factors for an Intermittent Power Resource or Limited Control Run of River Hydro Resource\n\nEach attachment covers specific aspects of capacity market operations and procedures.",
