        "id": "72a3339e-b93b-42b3-88fb-fbc1e2e1be01",
        "score": 0.47842973,
        "text": "The document page is from the NYISO Transmission Congestion Contracts Manual and lists various attachments related to Transmission Congestion Contracts (TCCs). These attachments are available on the NYISO website and are updated regularly. The attachments cover a range of topics, including:\n\n- Auction timelines and examples\n- Points of injection and withdrawal for centralized and reconfiguration auctions\n- Prohibited groups of points\n- Bidding rules\n- Binding agreements and purchase documents for non-historic and historic fixed price TCCs\n- Acronyms and abbreviations\n- Requests and notifications for incremental TCCs\n- Outage states and scheduling protocols\n- Sample notices and conversion documents\n\nAttachments A and B are reserved for future use.",
