      {
        "id": "419a19d2-95d8-4777-8f49-7c03a4ec87a1",
        "score": 0.45507196,
        "text": "The document page is from the NYISO Transmission Congestion Contracts Manual and outlines updates and revisions to various sections:\n\n- **Section 3.2.4**: Updated references in the TCC AMS User\u2019s Guide.\n- **Section 3.3.3**: Updated manual section references and replaced a report reference with the new TCC & Grandfathered Rights Report.\n- **Section 3.4.1**: Added modeling assumptions for Rainey and Blissville PARs and clarified optimization objectives.\n- **Section 3.4.5**: Updated the process description for requesting TCC Auction Data.\n- **Section 4.1.3**: Clarified revisions for \"Inventory ID\" and updated information sources.\n- **Section 4.1.7**: Clarified the section title.\n- **Section 4.4.5**: Updated manual section references.\n- **Section 4.8**: Revised the section title and updated the TCC Data Validation Certification Form.\n- **Sections 6.3.5, 6.6**: Removed references to \"merchant.\"\n- **Section 7**: Added procedures for Historic Fixed Price TCC extension products, reorganized provisions, and updated credit security requirements.\n- **Section 8**: Clarified eligible POIs for Non-Historic Fixed Price TCCs.\n- **Sections 8.1.6 and 8.3.6**: Updated credit security requirements for Non-Historic Fixed Price TCCs.\n- **Sections 8.1.10 and 8.3.10**: Updated sources for obtaining Nodal Price values.\n\nThe page also mentions \"Attachment T\" without further details.",
        "metadata": {
          "drive_path": "gs://tumeai-rag/NYISO/protocol/Transmission_Congestion_Contracts_Manual/page_15.jpg",
          "page_num": 15,
          "title": "Transmission Congestion Contracts Manual",
